	"summary": "libndp vulnerability",
	"details": "Julien Bernard discovered that libndp incorrectly performed origin checks\nwhen receiving Neighbor Discovery Protocol (NDP) messages. A remote\nattacker outside of the local network could use this issue to advertise a\nnode as a router, causing a denial of service, or possibly to act as a\nmachine-in-the-middle.",
